    dc:creator "Karar, Yasser F. M.; Blend, Charles K.; Dronen, Norman O.; Adel, Asmaa" ;
    dc:date "2023" ;
    dc:title "Towards resolving the problematic status of the digenean genus Astiotrema Looss 1900: Taxa excluded from Astiotrema (sensu stricto) with special reference to plagiorchioid genera closely related to the restricted concept of Astiotrema" ;
    fabio:hasPart <http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.7929527> ;
    a fabio:JournalArticle .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.7929527>
    dc:description "FIGURES 12 & 13. Alloastiotrema birmanii (Khan, Gul-E-Lala, Ghazi, Khatoon, Waheed & Khan, 2021) n. gen., n. comb. (syn. Astiotrema birmanii Khan, Gul-E-Lala, Ghazi, Khatoon, Waheed & Khan, 2021). 12. Al. birmanii, ventral view, redrawn from Khan et al. (2021, fig. 1). 13. Al. birmanii, ventral view, redrawn from Khan et al. (2021, fig. 2). Abbreviations: AT, anterior testis; Ce, cecum; CP, cirrus-pouch; Es, esophagus; GP, genital pore; OS, oral sucker; Ov, ovary; Ph, pharynx; PP, pars prostatica; PT, posterior testis; SV, seminal vesicle; Ut, uterus; VF, vitelline follicle; VS, ventral sucker. Scale bars: Fig. 12 = 300 µm; Fig. 13 = 300 µm." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/7929527/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

